      • hasChildNodes

        public boolean hasChildNodes()
        If this XMLDocument has a Valid Document Element (ie non-NULL), find if the Document has any children, then return TRUE. If the Document is NULL, or the Document has NO Children, then return FALSE.
        Returns:
        True if there are one (or more) Children of the document.
